{"tid":306522,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(劇透) (長文) 今晚打喪屍","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T06:48:34.000Z","uid":4322,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e334d0b21105c9ee04de750063f15214985682","tid":306522,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"早幾日個fd搵埋我一齊睇呢套野<br />\n係我衰 我無睇影評就出去 <br />\n（見係香港少見喪屍題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但大佬 睇完成套戲 都唔知佢講緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港產片無錯係要支持 <br />\n但你都唔好求求其其寫套野出黎<br />\n就搵一班演員咁畀心機咁做戲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你對唔對得住觀眾同演員<br />\nNo offence 我每次見到班演員好畀心機拍埋d鳩野 我感覺痛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢套野最大問題就係眼高手低 <br />\n打住香港近來少見既喪屍主題<br />\n(FYI 其實大部分時間都唔太關喪屍事)<br />\nOkay fine 如果你有message帶到出黎<br />\n但感覺只係好多野炒埋一碟 <br />\n喪屍只係閒角 隻雞又唔知做乜鳩<br />\n套戲無頭無尾 突然又彈個人出黎突然又彈d野出黎<br />\n坦白講 假如對白/劇情交代唔到 <br />\n你染染地用旁白我都收貨<br />\n你呢挺唔係叫留白/伏線 你呢d叫交代唔到咋！<br />\n會唔會其實focus多d落喪屍度？<br />\n但依家Cult又cult唔哂 好可惜<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想扁低任何人/任何港產片<br />\n相反 我想有進步 有進步就要有人講真話<br />\n我想有一套值得香港人驕傲既電影<br />\n雖然劇本係垃圾級別 但演員都係值得留意一下<br />\n見到萬子 白只 顏卓靈 都有唔少期待<br />\n假如呢個組合可以有一個正常劇本 應該可以幾有火花<br />\n另外加d漫畫/動畫落去 都可以幫手交代一d劇情<br />\n(畫出黎點都平過用染到仆街既特技 呢方面我欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nBtw, 呢套劇都其實仲包埋粵劇野入去 <br />\n但屌你都無好好利用 傳家之寶屌你拎去打怪都好 <br />\n<br />\n唉仆街砍掉重鍊喇個劇本 愛之深 責之切呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但王敏奕又真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385410483bd4b20933dd137119218cf7e461a119","tid":306522,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"咩叫染"},{"pid":"60b4618cd9a9e6c9eed754592b896812774b08f3","tid":306522,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"睇完成場係到屌 問睇左乜撚野"},{"pid":"662f144b49fdcf3f5a5e659f69d46a0da649367c","tid":306522,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完成場係到屌 問睇左乜撚野</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白白浪費左一班好有火花既演員"},{"pid":"94e8b24751a43a7f20cc86e6ba6d9604068fae39","tid":306522,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫染</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心定假腸"},{"pid":"f3463c74b0d28421ef538df7b3b380cc7d52caf2","tid":306522,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完成場係到屌 問睇左乜撚野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最撚chur係以為片尾有特別 屌"},{"pid":"d14f1207a2eacb2e0824cc7d53dc121496ab1247","tid":306522,"uid":23358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾到不得了 隻雞做乜尻"},{"pid":"00e27f2d1c17a0992ef928de8c99ec26135c8068","tid":306522,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾到不得了 隻雞做乜尻</blockquote><br />\n極同意！"},{"pid":"9ba2a734a2ba29aa7340e5341bf5b769c1f7e54c","tid":306522,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完成場係到屌 問睇左乜撚野</blockquote><br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白白浪費左一班好有火花既演員</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 正正常劇本應該有火花"},{"pid":"b0d6a1ae07d17bce7d24bf6eb0f871f887d4e6d5","tid":306522,"uid":45100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"其實睇得出真係好有心機，如音樂，服裝，化妝，動畫，演員，除左劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明個開局都唔錯，好多貌似伏線，點知有八成真係伏黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就奇怪點解其他野咁有心機，個劇本可以差到咁？番去查先知拍時有演員沒左影。但對個故仔影響有咁大架咩？"},{"pid":"c502087763f1dfb8f77b0fbd1d4bc253c7347714","tid":306522,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"港產喪屍。得生化壽屍好睇"},{"pid":"4f7cd7b057e78c7c9c23f6f9c861dc7ef69a2632","tid":306522,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"幾乎無打過喪屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻雞同d雞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想cult想隱喻都要大眾明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬子+白只扮結婚 &amp; 萬子死果兩幕有d感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘥曬個題材同d演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b1c2a3c23c933f37c1f17d6637fc97fc362bce","tid":306522,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港產喪屍。得生化壽屍好睇</blockquote><br />\n依套細細個睇,果陣好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到最後又會好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}